03:23.460 --> 03:26.380
At least some people agree with them. Some people don't.

03:26.380 --> 03:31.300
But I want to try and persuade you that it's not just hand waving.

03:31.300 --> 03:34.700
So how do we begin to think about it?

03:34.700 --> 03:40.460
