04:39.500 --> 04:45.780
Energy, metabolism, which is one of those words that tend to put a lot of people off,

04:45.780 --> 04:48.300
but I'll try and explain this as likely as I can.

04:48.300 --> 04:49.900
And then genetic information, genes.

04:49.900 --> 04:52.380
Where does information in biology come from?

04:52.380 --> 04:57.220
Which I think a lot of people find more interesting than metabolism.

04:57.220 --> 05:00.380
On the other hand, it can become quite obscure quite quickly.

05:00.380 --> 05:03.940
When you see the two together, it makes much more sense.

05:03.940 --> 05:07.780
So before I get going, I'm going to orientate you to those three themes.

05:07.780 --> 05:11.260
This is, you could think of this as a bacterial cell.

05:11.260 --> 05:15.180
