06:47.780 --> 06:50.260
has got an electrical charge equivalent to a bolt of lightning

06:50.260 --> 06:51.260
going across it.

06:51.260 --> 06:54.060
It's just such a small distance, five nanometres,

06:54.060 --> 06:57.300
that the actual charge is quite small.

06:57.300 --> 06:59.980
But it's quite a field strength.

06:59.980 --> 07:02.060
That is powering everything.

