08:40.460 --> 08:43.260
So it's not about energy only.

08:43.260 --> 08:45.100
It's also about biosynthesis.

08:45.100 --> 08:48.020
It's about making the building blocks of life.

08:48.020 --> 08:51.060
And this is again really deeply conserved in biology.

08:51.060 --> 08:52.860
Some of the molecules in that Krebs cycle,

08:52.860 --> 08:54.940
