09:16.740 --> 09:20.900
So it's kind of strange that both metabolism and energy

09:20.900 --> 09:22.380
are powered by the same system.

09:22.380 --> 09:25.260
There's a tension between which way is it going to go.

09:25.260 --> 09:28.340
