09:31.940 --> 09:34.660
going in the opposite direction, in this reverse direction,

09:34.660 --> 09:36.740
making the building blocks to make new cells

09:36.740 --> 09:40.260
to power the growth of cancer cells.

09:40.260 --> 09:44.060
So that's in a nutshell how metabolism is working.

