48:39.260 --> 48:42.380
So we have effectively the most hydrophobic base encodes,

48:42.380 --> 48:44.380
the most hydrophobic amino acid.

48:44.460 --> 48:47.380
And here we have a spartate, and it's encoded by a U,

48:47.380 --> 48:52.100
